<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-58-0011 </DOCNO><TEXT>The Tax Reform Act of 1986 (Act) makes major changes in the treatmentof cogeneration and alternative energy projects, and many of the significanttax advantages previously enjoyed by the cogeneration and alternativeenergy industries are lost under the Act. This paper summarizes the keyprovisions of the Act for cogeneration and alternative energy projects.</TEXT></DOC>